{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pullrequests/217/comments/131267343.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-common:9a444330c60e..b148f970bca4?path=graphics%2Fsrc%2Ftiny_obj_loader.h"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pull-requests/217/_/diff#comment-131267343"}}, "parent": {"id": 131266607, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pullrequests/217/comments/131266607.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pull-requests/217/_/diff#comment-131266607"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 217, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pullrequests/217.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/pull-requests/217"}}, "title": "tiny_obj_loader: default diffuse 0.625 instead of 0.6 to fix windows floating point warnings"}, "content": {"raw": "it's using type `real_t`, which can be `double` if the right macro is set:\n\n* #!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/src/9a444330c60e9f78ea5401d3bf8b3df83e8c1951/graphics/src/tiny_obj_loader.h#lines-125:131\n\nof course, this is our fork, and we control those macros, so we could use `0.6f`\n\nI thought `0.625` was clean, but I'm fine with `0.6f` if that's preferred", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>it's using type <code>real_t</code>, which can be <code>double</code> if the right macro is set:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/src/9a444330c60e9f78ea5401d3bf8b3df83e8c1951/graphics/src/tiny_obj_loader.h#lines-125:131\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/src/9a444330c60e9f78ea5401d3bf8b3df83e8c1951/graphics/src/tiny_obj_loader.h#lines-125:131</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>of course, this is our fork, and we control those macros, so we could use <code>0.6f</code></p>\n<p>I thought <code>0.625</code> was clean, but I'm fine with <code>0.6f</code> if that's preferred</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2020-01-10T21:42:18.270918+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": 1606, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "graphics/src/tiny_obj_loader.h"}, "updated_on": "2020-01-10T21:42:18.278534+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 131267343}